            "answer_text": "None. The questions have to be in the right order, so that they match the video slides back-projected onto the triptych of screens behind us. So I have a pile of cards with the questions and supplementary facts on them. During the afternoon I will have tried to familiarise myself as much as possible with the details of each question and answer so that I\u2019m not too dependent on the cards (bad TV if my face is lowered all the time!). But the others playing the game have no script and no advance sight of the questions. But note Kristian Carter's reply below\u2026 ",
